      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我先确认一下结构：起点是Track2 Data，终点是Encrypted Track2 Data，中间经过格式转换、BCD编码、填充，然后和Session Key汇合做加密。Session Key那边需要单独画一条准备路径吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
