      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Session Key要独立处理。它需要先应用Data Variant Mask，然后归一化成24字节的三重DES密钥格式。这个归一化节点要和填充后的数据一起进入加密环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SessionKey",
        "Normalize",
        "Pad",
        "Encrypt"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主流程搭出来：Track2 Data → Format Track2 → Convert to BCD → Pad to 8-byte blocks → 3DES Encryption → Encrypted Track2 Data。",
